name: Sketching Kit
description:
v1 - A small kit for your wireframe:

  1. Colors
  2. Text
  3. Icons
  4. Buttons
  5. Input (Text, Search, Date, Time)
  6. Checkbox, Radio, Switch
  7. Media Image, Media Video
  8. System iOS


Example:

  1. Log in
  2. Shop product
  3. Shopping bag
  4. Wallet
